node.text: My inner circe, sponsors and team were top of the range. They all gave me everything I would need to accomplish the goal.  I had to look in the mirror prior to the season, make the sacrifices needed, knowing it would be hard as hell and certainly not a lot of fun and loads of work on the front end.  I made that commitment because I wasn’t going to blame anyone for my short falls if I hadn’t won the title.  After it was said and done, those sacrifices were all well worth it on the back end.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Ricky Carmichael in Tallahassee, Florida. May be an image of text that says 'Special request school: to all you kids returning to not If you see someone who is struggling to make friends or being bullied because he/she doesn't have many friends or because they are shy or as pretty or not dressed in the most "in" clothes PLEASE step up. Say hi or at least smile at them in the hallway. You never know what that person might be facing outside of school. Your kindness might just make a BIG difference in someone's life! Parents and Grandparents should re-post this as well #StopBullying Thank you -RC'.

node.text: I’ve been posting this for a few years now and I hope it’s helping make a difference. School starts this week for some in Tallahassee so I wanted to send this reminder to all the kids and parents who are or will be starting school. This past year has been a little tougher than usual for some and I’m sure it’s been especially hard on some kids and their families. Let’s all try to be a little nicer to each other. This also goes for all you #keyboardwarriors out there. Please take a moment to talk to your kids about this and share if you agree. Thank you. #StopBullying #AntiBullying #BeNice
